## Tooling (dbt)

- `uv sync` — install Python deps (dbt-core + adapter) · `uv run dbt deps` — install dbt packages
- `uv run dbt build` — run + test models · `uv run dbt test` — tests only · `uv run dbt parse` — validate without a warehouse
- `uv run sqlfluff lint models/` — lint SQL · `uv run sqlfluff fix models/` — autofix
- Models live in `models/`. Dialect is configured in `.sqlfluff` (default: `snowflake`, templater `dbt`).
- The warehouse connection (`profiles.yml`) is environment-specific — keep credentials out of git; CI runs `dbt parse` until secrets are wired.
